Highlights
                    

                      

                        
M1 | FalleN - 3 AWP kills on the advanced bombsite A defense

M1 OT | VINI - 3 M4A1-S kills on the bombsite A retake (3vs3 post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M1 OT | sh1ro (CT) wins the 1vs2 situation (frag wise) but fails to keep Cloud9 in the running for Overpass as the bomb timer is not in their favor

                      

                      

                        
M2 | fer - 1vs2 clutch (CT - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | fnx - quick 1vs2 clutch (T - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | interz - 3 quick AK kills on the bombsite B defense to help Cloud9 reach map point

                      

                      

                        
M2 | HObbit - 3 quick M4A1-S kills on the bombsite B defense (clean round - vs buy) to secure the map victory for Cloud9

                      

                      

                        
M3 | boltz - quick 1vs2 clutch (CT - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M3 | fer - 3 Glock kills (2 HS) on the bombsite B bomb plant defense (second half pistol round)

                      

                      

                        
M3 | VINI - 2 quick AK kills on the bombsite A offensive (2vs2 situation) to secure the match victory for Imperial

"Cry is free" is one constantly used sentence to users who are complaining about something. But what most people doesn't know, is that this sentence is actually a huge lie.

As far as we know, tears consists of water and 0,9 gram salt per litre. And both of these ingredients are not free.

Here I listed the price of 10 litre tears for the countries of the G8.
I used the following formula (price is in US Dollar):

(price 100 gram salt/100)x9 + (price 1 cubic litre water/100) = price 10 litre tears

France: 0,20 $
Italy: 0,17 $
Germany: 0,19 $
United Kingdom: 0,22 $
USA: 0,18 $
Canada: 0,18 $
Japan: 0,18 $
Russia: 0,16 $

Thank you for reading.
